race.comment: IKIGAI (2) has been below best and missed the frame last couple, finishing 5th (17.62) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Dapto. Has a strong winning record here at this journey including three wins. Can discover winning form. HOUSIE BOB (1) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 3rd at this track over 400m. Expected to be in this for a long way. RIPPER LANE (3) has been a in top form recording back to back wins and both in best of the card, going 19.82 two back before 15.73 last time. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. OVERRIDING (7) is in the mix after placing last time out.
